    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      568.85,
      543.94,
      582.85
    ],
    "text": "excused; but not negligence, especially continuing negligence. The decision will",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      590.0,
      543.94,
      604.0
    ],
    "text": "depend on the facts and circumstances of each case. The Court will in granting",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      611.12,
      543.92,
      625.12
    ],
